5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20struggled%20to%20score%20runs%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20and%20things%20did%20not%20improve%20much%20during%20the%20Super%208%20encounter%20against%20Afghanistan%20on%20Thursday.%20Virat%20started%20his%20innings%20well%20but%20was%20dismissed%20by%20Rashid%20Khan%20after%20scoring%2024%20off%2024%20deliveries.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20steadied%20the%20innings%20and%20slammed%20a%20half-century%20to%20guide%20his%20team%20to%20a%20challenging%20total%20of%20181%2F8%20in%2020%20overs.%20During%20the%20innings%20break%2C%20Suryakumar%20opened%20up%20about%20how%20he%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20dressing%20room%20reacted%20to%20yet%20another%20disappointing%20show%20from%20Virat%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20I%20have%20practised%2C%20I%20enjoy%20batting%20from%20(7-15%20overs)%20that's%20the%20most%20difficult%20phase%20where%20the%20opposition%20bowlers%20look%20to%20control%20things.%20I%20like%20to%20take%20charge%20in%20that%20phase%2C%20I%20enjoy%20it.%20I%20started%20chewing%20my%20gum%20harder%20when%20he%20(Kohli)%20got%20out.%20I%20just%20backed%20my%20game%20and%20my%20instincts.%20I%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20with%20him%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20now%20under%20him%2C%20he%20understands%20my%20game.%20He%20knows%20my%20game%2C%20so%20he%20sits%20back%20and%20enjoys%20it.%20It's%20a%20good%20total%2C%20let's%20see%20what%20happens%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20during%20the%20mid%20innings%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20slammed%20a%20brilliant%20half-century%20before%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20took%20three%20wickets%20each%20to%20guide%20India%20to%20victory%20over%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20two%20years%2C%20we%20have%20come%20here%20and%20played%20some%20T20%20games.%20We%20planned%20a%20little%20well.%20We%20adapted%20well%20to%20the%20conditions%20that%20were%20offered.%20We%20knew%20the%20class%20of%20our%20bowling%20line%20up%20will%20defend%20this.%20Everyone%20coming%20in%20and%20doing%20their%20job.%20That%20is%20something%20we%20keep%20talking%20about.%20Surya%20and%20Hardik's%20partnership%20was%20a%20good%20one%20in%20the%20end.%20We%20know%20what%20Bumrah%20can%20do%20for%20us.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20us%20to%20use%20him%20smartly.%20He%20is%20the%20one%20who%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20responsibility%20as%20well.%20Whereever%20he%20plays%2C%20he%20is%20always%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20responsibility.%20I%20got%20to%20assess%20the%20conditions.%20Looking%20at%20the%20opposition%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20make%20any%20changes.%20We%20thought%20three%20spinners%20would%20be%20good%2C%20we%20went%20for%20that.%20Going%20forward%20if%20needed%2C%20I%20am%20open%20to%20playing%20three%20seamers%2C%26quot%3B%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718934420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fjh36c39_s_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fstarted-chewing-suryakumar-yadav-reveals-first-reaction-to-virat-kohlis-early-dismissal-5933653%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20team%20star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20struggled%20to%20score%20runs%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20and%20things%20did%20not%20improve%20much%20during%20the%20Super%208%20encounter%20against%20Afghanistan.%22%2C%22author