ar%20in%20my%20mind%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20just%20need%20to%20know%20your%20game%20plan%2C%20and%20just%20play%20accordingly.%20I%20still%20remember%20when%20Hardik%20came%20in%20to%20the%20bat%2C%20I%20told%20him%20let's%20bat%20with%20the%20same%20intent.%20Let's%20keep%20pressing%20the%20pedal%20and%20keep%20pushing%2C%20in%20the%20end%20very%20happy%20with%20a%20score%20of%20180.%26quot%3B%20PTI%20ATK%20KHS%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718930640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F63t24c6g_rohit-sharma-virat-kohli-afp_625x300_21_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fthats-critical-rohit-sharmas-blunt-take-after-indias-t20-world-cup-super-8-win-vs-afghanistan-5934310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20dishd%20out%20a%20superlative%20show%20as%20they%20posted%20181%20for%208%20and%20then%20returned%20to%20dismiss%20Afghanistan%20for%20134%20to%20register%20a%20comfortable%2047%20run%20win.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fthats-critical-rohit-sharmas-blunt-take-after-indias-t20-world-cup-super-8-win-vs-afghanistan-5934310%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fthats-critical-rohit-sharmas-blunt-take-after-indias-t20-world-cup-super-8-win-vs-afghanistan-5934310%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fthats-critical-rohit-sharmas-blunt-take-after-indias-t20-world-cup-super-8-win-vs-afghanistan-5934310%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RIP%20Donald%20Sutherland%3A%20Hollywood%20stars%20pay%20tribute%2