s%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fbest-school-notebook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elittle%20notebook%20for%20each%20kid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20I%20started%20writing%20short%20snippets%20about%20them%20whenever%20I%20could%20steal%20a%20minute.%20Early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20right%20before%20bed%2C%20during%20screen%20or%20naptime%2C%20I%20would%20jot%20down%20the%20date%20and%20a%20few%20details%20from%20their%20day%3A%20What%20was%20the%20weather%20like%2C%20and%20how%20did%20that%20impact%20our%20activities%3F%20What%20did%20they%20seem%20to%20think%20of%20our%20adventures%3F%20What%20new%20foods%20did%20they%20try%3F%20What%20did%20they%20learn%3F%20What%20did%20they%20say%3F%20Who%20did%20they%20meet%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22handwritten%20note%20by%20mom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66701d44e079049018197f04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20having%20these%20snippets%20now%20that%20her%20kids%20are%20teenagers%20is%20priceless.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20captured%20some%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-milestones-are-equally-important-as-baby-milestones-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebig%20milestones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20sitting%20up%2C%20rolling%20over%2C%20and%20first%20steps.%20Writing%20in%20a%20free%20format%20also%20gave%20me%20room%20to%20chronicle%20smaller%20developments%2C%20like%20the%20first%20time%20the%20kids%20saw%20a%20fireworks%20display%2C%20had%20an%20argument%2C%20went%20to%20a%20birthday%20party%2C%20took%20a%20solo%20trip%20down%20the%20slide%2C%20caught%20a%20ball%2C%20or%20got%20a%20time%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5b7d