ing%2C%20so%20I%20just%20signed%20whatever%20I%20needed%20to%20sign%20to%20start%20classes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnlike%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%20private%20loans%20are%20not%20covered%20by%20student%20loan%20forgiveness%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20fear%20that%20I'll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20own%20a%20home%20because%20of%20my%20student%20loans%2C%20but%20I'm%20focusing%20on%20solutions.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%3Fhprecirc-bullet%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2018%2C%20I%20was%20already%20overwhelmed%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20choices%20I%20needed%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20career%20path%20should%20I%20pursue%3F%20Which%20school%20will%20I%20choose%3F%20Do%20I%20go%20with%20the%20school%20that%20gave%20me%20the%20most%20scholarships%2C%20or%20the%20one%20that%20offers%20programs%20I'm%20more%20interested%20in%3F%20How%20am%20I%20going%20to%20mentally%2C%20emotionally%2C%20and%20physically%20prepare%20to%20move%20out%20of%20my%20parents'%20house%20for%20the%20first%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20that%20to%20think%20about%2C%20researching%20student%20loans%20was%20the%20last%20thing%20I%20wanted%20to%20think%20about.%20All%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20start%20building%20a%20career%20and%20a%20life%20that%20I%20was%20passionate%20about%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20According%20to%20my%20school%2C%20I%20was%20eligible%20for%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%20but%20they%20weren't%20enough%20to%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20my%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20my%20mom%20helped%20me%20by%20cosigning%20my%20student%20loans.%20However%2C%20reading%20financial%20jargon%20at%2018%20was%20really%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20I%20just%20signed%20whatever%20I%20needed%20to%20sign%20in%20order%20to%20start%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20signing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-private-student-loans%5C%22%3Eprivate%20student%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%20changed%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20have%20barely%20made%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20principal%20amount%20of%20the%20loan%2010%20years%20later%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20I%20was%20too%20ashamed%20and%20guilty%20about%20my%20circumstances%20to%20even%C2%A0%3Cem%3Elook%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20my%20Navient%20account.%20Once%20I%20finally%20checked%20it%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20the%20principal%20balance%20had%20actually%20increased%2C%20even%20though%20I%20had%20been%20making%20regular%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20went%20through%20financial%20hardship%2C%20I%20put%20my%20loans%20in%20forbearance%20for%20a%20few%20months.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20my%20loans%20racked%20up%20capitalized%20interest.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20if%20my%20mom's%20credit%20wasn't%20on%20the%20line%2C%20I%20would%20opt%20out%20of%20paying%20my%20Navient%20bill%20just%20to%20build%20myself%20a%20healthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-student-loan-refinance-companies%5C%22%3EStudent%20loan%20refinancing%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20lower%20your%20interest%20rate%20and%20help%20you%20pay%20down%20your%20loan%20faster.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans-marketplace%5C%22%3EGet%20prequalified%20without%20impacting%20your%20credit%20score%20today.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20afraid%20I'll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20save%20for%20big%20milestones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20my%20monthly%20payments%20are%20so%20high%2C%20I'm%20afraid%20I'll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20or%20start%20my%20own%20family.%20Every%20time%20I%20make%20my%20monthly%20payments%2C%20I%20fantasize%20about%20how%20I%20can%20use%20th