re%20of%20the%20ruling%20DMK.%20They%20have%20also%20blamed%20the%20police%20and%20asked%20if%20there%20was%20an%20intelligence%20failure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20Chief%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BChief%20Minister%20Stalin%20should%20resign.%20This%20is%20incompetence.%20He%20gives%20an%20excuse%20every%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20different%20tack%2C%20K%20Annamalai%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%2C%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20should%20close%20at%20least%20a%20thousand%20liquor%20shops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20did%20not%20visit%20the%20affected%20areas%20but%20sent%20ministers%2C%20including%20his%20son%20Udhayanidhi.%20Calling%20the%20incident%20painful%20and%20sad%2C%20he%20assured%20a%20crackdown%20and%20announced%20a%20one-man%20commission%20to%20conduct%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20accident.%20The%20home%20secretary%20and%20the%20DGP%20are%20expected%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20in%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20of%20liquor%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20fetches%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20in%20revenue.%20That%20indicates%20the%20level%20of%20alcohol%20addiction%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20DMK%20had%20argued%20that%20total%20prohibition%20would%20only%20open%20the%20floodgates%20of%20illicit%20liquor.%20Now%2C%20many%20are%20asking%20if%20it%20is%20time%20for%20a%20relook%20at%20the%20alcohol%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718907000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5oh3dero_tamil-nadu-hooch-tragedy-_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-hooch-tragedy-hit-tamil-nadu-village-queue-of-bodies-at-cremation-ground-5934089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20pall%20of%20gloom%20has%20descended%20over%20Karunapuram%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Kallakurichi%20district.%20As%20many%20as%2024%20of%20the%2039%20w