xkmgdro.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Acted%20On%20Unsecured%20Loans%20To%20Avert%20Bigger%20Problems%3A%20RBI%20Governor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20endeavors%20to%20smell%20out%20a%20crisis%20early%20and%20act%20on%20it%2C%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%2C%20stating%20that%20not%20taking%20any%20action%20on%20the%20unsecured%20lending%20front%20would%20have%20created%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20problems%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20November%202023%20action%20to%20curb%20growth%20in%20the%20riskier%20unsecured%20lending%20has%20had%20the%20desired%20impact%20as%20the%20growth%20in%20such%20portfolios%20slowed%20down%2C%20Mr%20Das%20said%20addressing%20an%20international%20conference%20on%20financial%20resilience%20at%20the%20RBI's%20College%20of%20Supervisors%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestrictions%20on%20unsecured%20lending%20were%20the%20result%20of%20a%20view%20that%20there%20could%20be%20a%20potential%20problem%20in%20the%20credit%20market%20because%20of%20growth%20in%20unsecured%20lending%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20headline%20parameters%20were%20looking%20good%2C%20but%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bclear%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20dilution%20of%20underwriting%20standards%2C%20lack%20of%20proper%20appraisals%2C%20and%20a%20mentality%20to%20join%20the%20bandwagon%20for%20driving%20up%20the%20unsecured%20lending%20among%20some%20lenders%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20if%20left%20unattended%2C%20these%20vulnerabilities%20can%20become%20a%20bigger%20problem.%20So%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20is%20better%20to%20act%20in%20advance%20and%20slow%20down%20the%20credit%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20satisfaction%20that%20the%20RBI's%20action%20has%20had%20the%20desired%20impact%2C%20as%20the%20growth%20in%20unsecured%20lending%20has%20indeed%20slowed%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growth%20in%20credit%20card%20portfolios%20slowed%20down%20to%2023%25%20from%2030%25%20before%20the%20RBI's%20action%2C%20while%20the%20growth%20in%20bank%20lending%20to%20Non-Banking%20Finance%20Companies%20(NBFC)%20has%20slowed%20to%2018%25%20from%20the%20earlier%2029%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2016%20last%20year%2C%20the%20RBI%20increased%20risk%20weights%20on%20unsecured%20lending%20and%20exposure%20to%20NBFCs%2C%20which%20made%20banks%20set%20aside%20larger%20amounts%20of%20capital%20on%20such%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%2C%20who%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20central%20bank%20for%20over%20five%20years%20now%2C%20said%20that%20the%20RBI%20shifted%20its%20approach%20to%20be%20as%20proactive%20as%20possible%20to%20ensure%20systemic%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20afford%20to%20say%20that%20we%20are%20smelling%20a%20crisis%20on%20every%20occasion%20but%20it%20is%20our%20endeavour%20to%20smell%20out%20a%20crisis.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20our%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20agenda%20is%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20RBI's%20mind%20all%20the%20time%20-%20to%20see%20if%20something%20is%20building%20up%20either%20at%20the%20systemic%20level%20or%20at%20an%20individual%20organisation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20asked%20lenders%20to%20look%20beyond%20%26quot%3Bmindless%26quot%3B%20growth%20in%20profits%20and%20keep%20other%20factors%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20business%20models%20may%20be%20designed%20to%20drive%20profitability%20and%20growth%2C%20they%20sometimes%20contain%20vulnerabilities%20that%20may%20not%20be%20apparent.%20Pursuit%20of%20business%20growth%20is%20important%2C%20but%20it%20should%20never%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20taking%20on%20unacceptable%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20YES%20Bank%20bailout%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20RBI%20had%20been%20watching%20developments%20at%20the%20bank%20closely%20since%20late%202018%20and%20had%20to%20launch%20the%20multi-agency%20bailout%20in%20March%202020%2C%20just%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20domestic%20financial%20system%20is%20now%20in%20a%20much%20stronger%20position%20than%20it%20was%20before%20we%20entered%20the%20period%20of%20the%20COVID%20crisis.%20The%20Indian%20financial%20system%20is%20now%20in%20a%20much%20stronger%20position%2C%20characterised%20by%20robust%20capital%20adequacy%2C%20low%20levels%20of%20non-performing%20assets%2C%20and%20healthy%20profitability%20of%20banks%20and%20non-banking%20lenders%2C%20or%20NBFCs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20has%20undertaken%20a%20slew%20of%20efforts%20to%20increase%20its%20supervisory%20function%2C%20including%20making%20a%20provision%20of%20a%20detailed%20presentation%20to%20a%20bank%20board%20by%20an%20executive%20director%20if%20it%20finds%20something%20amiss%20and%20also%20meeting%20the%20auditors%20of%20a%20bank%20if%20it%20feels%20the%20need%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20onsite%20supervision%20of%20credit%20information%20companies%20has%20been%20made%20%26quot%3Bannual%20and%20intense%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20RBI%20governor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718906280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8mcuij48_rbi-governor-shaktikanta-das-ani_625x300_08_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Facted-on-unsecured-loans-to-avert-bigger-problems-rbi-governor-shaktikanta-das-5932607%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20endeavors%20to%20smell%20out%20a%20crisis%20early%20and%20act%20on%20it%2C%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said