0money%20to%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20they%20asked%20to%20download%20Skype%20and%20will%20record%20a%20statement%20from%20me%20on%20video%20call.%20They%20also%20asked%20for%20my%20Aadhaar%2C%20and%20told%20me%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20separate%20room%20so%20that%20no%20one%20interferes%20during%20the%20police%20investigation%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20'officer'%20told%20her%20to%20send%20the%20money%20in%20her%20bank%20account%20to%20be%20verified%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20after%20which%20it%20will%20be%20returned%20in%2015%20minutes%20following%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20issued%20an%20acknowledgement%20letter%20that%20I%20am%20a%20suspect%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20and%20if%20I%20won't%20transfer%20the%20funds%20they%20will%20take%20me%20into%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20she%20sent%20Rs%2051%2C000%20from%20her%20ICICI%20Bank%20account%20to%20an%20account%20in%20IndusInd%20Bank%20named%20'Sri%20Lalita%20Agency'%20based%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Vijayawada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdpomabbo_fake-cop_625x300_20_June_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20realised%20the%20fraud%2C%20she%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20on%20the%20cyber%20crime%20portal.%20She%20blocked%20her%20internet%20banking%20ID%20and%20informed%20the%20bank%20about%20the%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20Cases%20Across%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20such%20cases%20in%20which%20the%20criminals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%