awyer%20had%20said%20earlier%20today%2C%20after%20which%20the%20court%20had%20reserved%20its%20order%2C%20only%20to%20announce%20the%20bail%20around%208%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCircumstances%20have%20to%20be%20so%20intrinsically%20linked%20(as%20to)%20lead%20to%20the%20guilt.%20These%20statements%20by%20tainted%20persons%20discredit%20the%20case%20of%20prosecution.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20Rs%20100%20crore%20came%20from%20'South%20Group'.%20These%20are%20all%20statements.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20lawyer%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20what%20the%20ED%20calls%20the%20'South%20Group'%2C%20a%20lobby%20from%20Telangana%20that%20allegedly%20conspired%20to%20grab%20liquor%20licences%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20March%2021%20over%20money%20laundering%20allegations%20while%20framing%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20for%202021-22%2C%20which%20was%20later%20scrapped%20after%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20raised%20red%20flags.%20The%20ED%20has%20alleged%20the%20money%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20got%20from%20the%20liquor%20sellers%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20party's%20campaign%20in%20Goa%2C%20since%20he%20is%20the%20convenor%20of%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20and%20the%20AAP%20have%20from%20the%20start%20maintained%20the%20Centre%20has%20been%20misusing%20its%20agencies%20to%20harass%20the%20Opposition%20with%20false%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718899380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flb3g75f8_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_02_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-gets-bail-in-liquor-policy-case-5932626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22h