22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmore-than-1-000-dead-during-hajj-as-heatwaves-spread-across-the-world-13156146%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmore-than-1-000-dead-during-hajj-as-heatwaves-spread-across-the-world-13156146%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BForming%20High-Level%20Committee%2C%20Won't%20Spare%20Anyone%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister%20On%20Exams%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%20for%20the%20irregularities%20in%20NEET%20and%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20has%20said%20that%20a%20high-level%20committee%20will%20be%20formed%20and%20that%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20students%20is%20the%20first%20priority%20of%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2030%20lakh%20candidates%20appeared%20for%20the%20exams%2C%20both%20of%20which%20were%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20and%20the%20minister's%20comments%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20students%20held%20protests%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20outside%20Mr%20Pradhan's%20home%20in%20Delhi.%20Some%20were%20also%20detained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20everyone%20that%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20the%20interests%20of%20students.%20We%20will%20not%20compromise%20with%20that%20or%20with%20transparency.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20NEET%20exams%20are%20concerned%2C%20we%20are%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20the%20Bihar%20government%20and%20the%20Patna%20Police%20will%20send%20us%20a%20detailed%20report%20soon.%20As%20per%20preliminary%20information%2C%20errors%20are%20limited%20to%20certain%20regions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20reference%20was%20to%20reports%20of%20the%20NEET%20paper%20being%20leaked%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20that%2C%20once%20we%20get%20concrete%20evidence%2C%20none%20of%20the%20guilty%20will%20be%20spared%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20NTA%20or%20some%20senior%20NTA%20official.%20Our%20priority%20is%20the%20future%20of%20students.%20The%20government%20is%20also%20setting%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee.%20It%20will%20give%20recommendations%20on%20improving%20NTA's%20structure%2C%20its%20functioning%2C%20examination%20process%2C%20transparency%20and%20data%2C%20and%20security%20protocol.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20zero-error%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20consist%20of%20technocrats%2C%20scientists%2C%20education%20administrators%2C%20academicians%20and%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20government%20had%20brought%20in%20a%20law%20to%20prevent%20the%20use%20of%20unfair%20means%20in%20public%20examinations%2C%20the%20minister%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20not%20spread%20rumours%20on%20such%20issues%20or%20politicise%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLakhs%20of%20students%2C%20many%20of%20them%20meritorious%20candidates%20who%20are%20poor%20or%20from%20rural%20areas%2C%20have%20got%20good%20marks%20and%20good%20ranks.%20Their%20career%20should%20not%20be%20held%20hostage%20because%20of%20isolated%20incidents.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20make%20all%20needed%20improvements.%20None%20of%20the%20guilty%20will%20be%20spared%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20-%20which%20is%20held%20for%20Assistant%20Professor%20posts%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%20and%20to%20determine%20eligibility%20for%20junior%20research%20fellowships%20-%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20when%20the%20UGC%20chairman%20received%20information%20from%20the%20cyber%20crime%20team%20in%20the%20home%20ministry%20about%20questions%20being%20on%20the%20darknet%2C%20tallying%20was%20done%20with%20the%20original%20paper%20and%20an%20immediate%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20hold%20a%20CBI%20investigation.%20It%20was%20also%20decided%20to%20cancel%20the%20exam%20after%20it%20was%20established%20that%20its%20integrity%20had%20been%20compromised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Taking%20Responsibility'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20government%20would%20cancel%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20because%20some%20students%20have%20said%20that%20they%20received%20leaked%20papers%20a%20day%20before%20the%20test%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20that%20the%20government%20has%20to%20keep%20the%20interests%20of%20meritorious%20students%20in%20mind%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressed%20on%20the%20UGC-NET%20issue%20and%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20students%20who%20will%20have%20to%20reappear%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20taking%20responsibility.%20We%20have%20to%20rectify%20the%20system.%20We%20will%20come%20out%20with%20dates%20very%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20he%20is%20taking%20moral%20responsibility%20for%20the%20NEET%20matter%20and%20is%20not%20trying%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20doing%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718896680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fn1a7u87g_dharmendra-pradhan-ani_625x300_13_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fforming-high-level-committee-education-minister-dharmendra-pradhan-on-exam-row-5932450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20fire%20for%20the%20irregularities%20in%20NEET%20and%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20has%20said%20that%20a%20high-level%20committee%20will%20be%20formed%20and%20that%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20students%20is%20the%20government's%20first%20priority.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canoni