his%20own%20life%20to%20being%20out%20and%20proud%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20his%20incredible%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Choosing%20myself%20helped%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20his%20early%20childhood%2C%20Srivatsan%20knew%20that%20he%20was%20different.%20He%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20with%20his%20cousin%20sisters%20than%20his%20brothers.%20His%20first%20crush%20was%20on%20a%20blue-eyed%20boy%20with%20curly%20hair.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hated%20playing%20cricket%20in%20the%20hot%20sun%2C%20especially%20fielding%3B%20this%20was%20my%20first%20clue.%20Also%20I%20just%20always%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20something%20different%20about%20me.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20relate%20to%20the%20boys%20in%20class%20and%20over%20time%2C%20I%20understood%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F294409%2Fi-am-gay-brothers-ashish-vishesh-chopra-coming-out-story-raksha-bandhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20was%20gay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201195px)%20100vw%2C%201195px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri3-1718194184.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221195%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srivatsan%20and%20Saravanan%20met%20in%20Singapore%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri3-1718194184.jpeg%201195w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri3-1718194184-224x300.jpeg%20224w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri3-1718194184-500x669.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri3-1718194184-768x1028.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri3-1718194184-1147x1