nt%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20solving%20some%20of%20the%20persistent%20challenges%20in%20vegetable%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20organic%20journey%20leading%20to%20a%20patented%20grow%20bag%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%20was%20first%20introduced%20to%20organic%20farming%20while%20still%20in%20Malabar%2C%20where%20he%20experimented%20with%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20determine%20what%20worked%20best%20for%20various%20crops.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20he%20expanded%20his%20organic%20farming%20practices%20to%20include%20livestock.%20On%20his%20three-acre%20farm%2C%20cows%20and%20goats%20coexist%20with%20vegetables.%20He%20notes%20that%20cow%20dung%20serves%20as%20an%20excellent%20fertiliser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20consuming%20the%20vegetables%20that%20were%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Reading%20about%20the%20ill%20effects%20of%20consuming%20food%20with%20pesticides%20prompted%20me%20to%20start%20growing%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eyyo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296470%2Faward-winning-kerala-terrace-farmer-grows-seasonal-veggies-zucchini-cauliflower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20typically%20used%20for%20indoor%20farming%2C%20the%20septuagenarian%20decided%20to%20try%20them%20outdoors.%20His%20initial%20experiments%20with%20traditional%20plastic%20grow%20bags%20were%20unsatisfactory.%20Concurrently%2C%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20rampant%20disposal%20of%20plastic%20bottles.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20wonder%20%E2%80%94%20could%20a%20plastic%20bottle%20be%20used%20to%20water%20his%20plants%20slowly%2C%20mimicking%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system%3F%20The%20answer%20he%20discovered%20was%20a%20resounding%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20initially%20began%20by%20modi