he%20bottom%20and%20sides%20for%20excess%20water%20drainage.%20It%20is%20spacious%20enough%20to%20allow%20plants%20to%20grow%20freely.%20To%20use%20it%2C%20you%20fill%20a%20water%20bottle%2C%20turn%20it%20upside%20down%2C%20and%20quickly%20place%20it%20in%20the%20hole%20to%20prevent%20leakage.%20The%20farmer%20advises%20ensuring%20no%20air%20enters%20the%20bottle%20while%20pressing%20it%20into%20the%20soil.%20This%20method%20ensures%20that%20water%20is%20directed%20precisely%20to%20the%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20reduces%20water%20wastage%20and%20secures%20a%20consistent%20supply%20of%20moisture%20to%20the%20plant%20roots.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20leave%20the%20bottle%20after%20inserting.%20The%20water%20will%20slowly%20percolate%20as%20per%20the%20requirement.%20I%20generally%20use%20a%20one-litre%20bottle%2C%20which%20suffices%20for%20at%20least%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Eyyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20provides%20an%20optimum%20use%20of%20plastic%20water%20bottles.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20many%20use%20this%20method%2C%20we%20can%20prevent%20many%20plastic%20bottles%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%20prepares%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288760%2Fhow-to-grow-organic-ginger-in-grow-bags-and-sacks-kerala-farmer-shares-steps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20mix%20for%20his%20grow%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20starts%20by%20ploughing%20some%20topsoil%20and%20mixing%20in%20some%20lime%20powder%20(%3Cem%3Ekummayam%3C%2Fem%3E).%20He%20then%20leaves%20this%20mixture%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20for%2010%20days%2C%20regularly%20sprinkling%20water%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20prepares%20another%20mixture%20using%20powdered%20cow%20dung%2C%20powdered%20bone%20meal%20(%3Cem%3Eellupodi%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20neem%20press%20cake%20(%3Cem%3Evep%20pinnakku%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20groundnut%20cake%20(%3Cem%3Ekadala%20pinnakku%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20trichoderma%2C%20and%20super%20phosphate%20or%20mussoorie%20phos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mixture%20is%20stirred%20daily%20for%20six%20to%20seven%20days%2C%20with%20water%20added%20periodically.%20Finally%2C%20the%20two%20mixtures%20are%20combined%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grow%20bag%20is%20designed%20so%20that%20the%20mixture%20does%20not%20come%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20soil%20beneath%2C%20effectively%20preventing%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%20from%20spreading.%20Eyyo%20shares%20that%20this%20grow%20bag%20is%20patented%20and%20much%20more%20durable%20than%20standard%20ones%2C%20lasting%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20potentially%20even%20longer%20when%20used%20in%20home%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20bag%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20461px)%20100vw%2C%20461px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%20461w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-150x333.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692.jpeg%20576w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20grow%20bags%2C%20Eyyo%20has%20developed%20a%20UV%20sheet%20that%20can%20protect%20crops%20from%20harsh%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20an%20innovative%20farmer%2C%20Eyyo%20is%20a%20generous%20teacher%20who%20loves%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge.%20Although%20he%20has%20reduced%20his%20farming%20activities%20with%20age%2C%20he%20is%20always%20happy%20to%20host%20visitors%20and%20provide%20tips%20on%20organic%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20important%20to%20consume%20organic%20food.%20Be%20mindful%20of%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20eating%3B%20try%20to%20grow%20some%20basic%20vegetables%20at%20home.%20Use%20neem%20as%20a%20fertiliser%20for%20your%20kitchen%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Eyyo%20Kuriakose%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718115897000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%2078%2C%20Eyyo%20Kuriakose%20from%20Kottayam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20has%20developed%20a%20patented%2C%20durable%20grow%20bag%20with%20an%20integrated%20drip%20irrigation%20system%2C%20which%20he%20claims%20reduces%20water%20usage%20and%20enhances%20crop%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F352674%2Fgrow-bags-growing-vegetables-eyyo-kuriakose-kottayam-kerala-organic-farming-drip-irrigation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineers%20Design%20100%25%20Solar%20EV%20Tricycle%20For%20Goods%20%26amp%3B%20Waste%20Transport%3B%20Can%20Carry%20Up%20to%20300%20Kg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20June%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%23ApnaGharSolar%20series%2C%20an%20exclusive%20deep%20dive%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsocialmedia%26utm_medium%3Dad%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20solar%20power%20boom.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20more%20interesting%20stories%2C%20data%20and%20information!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world%2C%20and%20particularly%20India%2C%20embraces%20the%20concept%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231562%2Fsustainable-living-experiments-activities-children-the-better-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20living%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20numerous%20alternatives%20have%20emerged%20across%20various%20sectors.%20A%20notable%20example%20of%20this%20shift%20is%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20companies%20and%20innovators%20introducing%20newer%20and%20more%20efficient%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20the%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20tremendous%20rate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20India%20electric%20vehicle%20market%20size%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%20from%20USD%203.21%20billion%20in%202022%20to%20USD%20113.99%20billion%20in%202029%2C%20growing%20at%20a%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2066.52%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EFortune%20Business%20Insights.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJumping%20on%20the%20bandwagon%20are%20three%20young%20and%20innovative%20minds%20hailing%20from%20Kerala.%20Jacob%20Thekkekara%2C%20Azim%20Hashmi%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Hadi%20Mutheri%2C%20with%20their%20Kochi-based%20company%20Sugrah%20Mobility%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20have%20developed%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20solar-powered%20electric%20three-vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20while%20there%20were%20e-rickshaws%2C%20there%20were%20not%20any%20with%20a%20load-bearing%20capacity%20for%20transporting%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jacob%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Sugrah%20Mobility%20and%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20tricycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvailable%20for%20sale%20in%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F258975%2Findia-student-innovation-solar-electric-tricycle-smart-kisok-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tricycle%20is%20not%20just%20electric%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20100%20percent%20solar-run.%20He%20talks%20about%20the%20innovation%2C%20the%20idea%20behind%20it%2C%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%20in%20their%20plan%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20sustainable%20approach%20to%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESugrah%20is%20co-founder%20of%20Jacob%E2%80%99s%20second%20stint%20at%20business.%20While%20he%20founded%20another%20company%20on%20similar%20lines%20earlier%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20on%20doing%20something%20in%20his%20home%20state.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20along%20the%20same%20lines%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20which%20was%20more%20tangible%20and%20had%20a%20real%20impact.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20that%20startup%20and%20look%20for%20something%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudying%20markets%2C%20Jacob%20realised%20how%20the%20country%20depends%20a%20lot%20on%20three-wheelers%20for%20low%20to%20medium-scale%20transportation.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20odd%20%3Cem%3Ejugaads%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20many%20three-wheeler%20owners%20have%20done%20such%20as%20making%20it%20mechanical%20from%20a%20local%20mechanic.%20However%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20those%20can%20be%20dangerous%20and%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20such%20innovations%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20three-wheeler%20EVs%20with%20a%20good%20load-bearing%20capacity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20the%20potential%20of%20a%20product%20like%20that%20and%20decided%20to%20head%20in%20the%20same%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tricycle%20can%20be%20used%20for%20advertisement%20purposes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352637%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20tricycle%20can%20be%20used%20for%20advertisement%20purposes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mechanical%20engineer%20with%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20from%20IIT-Madras%2C%20Jacob%20was%20joined%20by%20his%20engineer%20friends%2C%20Azim%20and%20Abdul%2C%20who%20had%20a%20similar%20vision.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20group%20started%20to%20brainstorm%20and%20research%20process.%20The%20company%20was%20founded%20the%20same%20year%2C%20whereas%20the%20tricycle%20was%20eventually%20launched%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETo%20bear%20the%20load%20of%20Indian%20transportation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20peddle-assisted%20three-wheeler%20can%20carry%20up%20to%20300%20kg%20of%20weight.%20Jacob%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20various%20features%2C%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20the%20only%20company%20that%20provides%20a%20working%20solar-powered%20three-wheeler%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%20For%20a%20solar-powered%20vehicle%20to%20run%20about%20100%20km%20a%20day%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20pedal-assisted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20runs%20entirely%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CFor%20an%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20we%20typically%20need%20to%20charge%20it%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20resulting%20in%20around%2019%20gm%20of%20CO2%20emissions%20per%20passenger%20per%20kilometre.%20However%2C%20by%20using%20solar%20power%20to%20generate%20electricity%2C%20this%20emission%20was%20reduced%20drastically%20to%20just%200.5%20gm.%20This%20demonstrates%20a%20significant%20reduction%20in%20CO2%20emissions%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20operate%20the%20vehicle%20on%20100%20percent%20solar%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CComparatively%2C%20our%20vehicle%20saves%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20CO2%20emissions%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20electric%20vehicles.%20We%20utilise%20gas-powered%20generators%20to%20generate%20energy%2C%20thereby%20eliminating%20any%20additional%20carbon%20footprint.%20This%20is%20a%20standout%20feature%20that%20we%20proudly%20boast%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20is%20also%20a%20bio-hybrid%2C%20meaning%20it%20can%20be%20charged%20both%20by%20pedal%20and%20by%20the%20portal.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20the%20battery%20is%20depleted%20and%20you%20do%20not%20have%20a%20source%20to%20charge%20it%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20pedal%20the%20vehicle%20and%20it%20will%20be%20recharged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20company%20also%20offers%20variable%20gears.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20allowing%20users%20to%20shift%20to%20higher%20gears%20for%20heavier%20loads%20and%20lower%20gears%20for%20lighter%20loads%2C%20enabling%20faster%20movement.%20Additionally%2C%20all-wheel%20braking%20and%20robust%20tyres%20are%20provided%20with%20the%20vehicles.%20To%20maintain%20a%20lightweight%20yet%20sturdy%20structure%2C%20the%20vehicle%20features%20lightweight%20aluminium%20panels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-17-1718106029.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tricycle%20runs%20fully%20on%20solar%20power.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-17-1718106029.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-17-1718106029-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-17-1718106029-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-17-1718106029-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-17-1718106029-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352638%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20tricycle%20runs%20fully%20on%20solar%20power.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20features%20collectively%20make%20this%20peddle-assisted%20three-wheeler%20a%20sustainable%20and%20efficient%20choice%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20discussing%20the%20target%20audience%20for%20his%20innovation%2C%20Jacob%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20our%20product%20is%20designed%20for%20small%20business%20owners%20seeking%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F40151%2Felectric-buses-in-gujarat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20sustainable%20transportation%3C%2Fa%3E%20solutions.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20suitable%20for%20large%20factory%20owners%20who%20can%20utilise%20it%20within%20their%20facilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20vehicle%20can%20be%20used%20effectively%20inside%20warehouses%20for%20transporting%20goods%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20ideal%20for%20food%20and%20vegetable%20vendors.%20We%20also%20envision%20its%20potential%20in%20garbage%20collection.%20Imagine%20the%20logistical%20challenge%20of%20charging%2013%2C000%20e-rickshaws%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F162019%2Finnovation-garbage-collection-cart-uttar-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20garbage%20collection%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Chennai.%20This%20scenario%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20significant%20failure.%20This%20is%20where%20our%20fully%20solar-powered%20vehicles%20come%20into%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20innovation%20is%20now%20a%20finished%20product%2C%20Jacob%20recalls%20that%20figuring%20out%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20the%20product%20was%20a%20nightmare%20for%20the%20team.%20%E2%80%9CStarting%20something%20from%20scratch%20is%20always%20challenging%20but%20a%20lack%20of%20existing%20infrastructure%20in%20terms%20of%20supply%20chain%20made%20our%20operations%20a%20little%20difficult.%20We%20went%20to%20various%20vendors%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20tried%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20needed%20and%20then%20figured%20out%20how%20we%20can%20make%20it%20available%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5