ations%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20solar-powered%20EV.%20After%20two%20months%20of%20usage%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20reliable%20and%20eco-friendly%20choice.%20Kudos%20to%20the%20company%20for%20providing%20such%20a%20fantastic%20electric%20vehicle%20with%20so%20many%20utilitarian%20features.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solar-powered%20vehicle%20is%20priced%20starting%20Rs%201%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%20the%20electric%20variant%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%201%2C50%2C000%20and%20the%20manual%20variant%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2030%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20book%20your%20ride%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sugrah.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Sugrah%20Mobility%20Pvt%20Ltd)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718114935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352632%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Co-founded%20by%20Jacob%20Thekkekara%2C%20Azim%20Hashmi%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Hadi%20Mutheri%2C%20Kochi-based%20Sugrah%20Mobility%20Pvt%20Ltd%20has%20introduced%20a%20solar-powered%20electric%20three-wheeler%20designed%20for%20commercial%20use%2C%20particularly%20for%20small%20businesses%20and%20factories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352632%2Fiit-madras-jacob-thekkekara-sugrah-mobility-ev-solar-powered-tricycle-kochi-kerala%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waffle%20House%20Is%20Raising%20Servers'%20Pay%20Across%20The%20Country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20restaurant%20chain's%20CEO%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%26quot%3B%20invest